# beads Codex Runtime Snippet

## Session Start

Always run:

```bash
bd dolt pull || true
bd prime
bd ready --json
```

## Claim Protocol

Claim before starting work:

```bash
bd show <issue-id>
bd update <issue-id> --claim
```

## Discovery Protocol

For newly discovered work, create a bead and link it with `discovered-from`:

```bash
bd create "<title>" -t task -p 2 --json
bd dep add <new-id> <current-id> --type discovered-from
```

## Handoff Protocol

At session end, update notes and push (if remote is configured):

```bash
bd update <issue-id> --notes "COMPLETED: ...\nIN PROGRESS: ...\nNEXT: ..."
bd dolt push || true
```
